{"id":"errors/NG0507","title":"NG0507: 伺服器端渲染後 HTML 內容被修改","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exhgo1drwks5j7wencgbrb5h1\">NG0507: 伺服器端渲染後 HTML 內容被修改<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3sv8mf31m91khwxnf6mnlnzyy\">當Angular檢測到伺服器端渲染（SSR）生成的內容在渲染後被更改時，將引發此錯誤。水合過程依賴於在SSR後內容保持不變，其中包括空格和註解節點。這些空格和註解節點必須在SSR過程生成的HTML中保留。在\n<a href=\"guide/hydration#constraints\">水合指南</a>中瞭解更多訊息。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0507#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9suv0130vftmw2dfsxdapnru8\">通常發生在以下情況下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4lk8jmxnyw93qt4wuoh0mhd8d\">一些CDN提供商內建了刪除HTML中空格和註解節點的功能作為最佳化選項。請驗證CDN設定中是否有這樣的選項，並將其關閉。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5jix7lmhufmcpf14ysz3i3ww1\">如果您對SSR生成的HTML進行自定義後處理（作為建立步驟），請確保此過程不會刪除空格和註解節點。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - errors/NG0507#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG0507#description\n - errors/NG0507#ng0507-html-content-was-altered-after-server-side-rendering\n - guide/hydration#constraints\n-->"}